title: adidas Originals Unleashes the Cleanest EQT Support Ultra Yet
text:
Visit the original post to see all 2 images from this gallery. 
Brand : adidas Originals.
Model : EQT Support Ultra.
Key Features : adidas Originals continues to roll out its popular EQT Support Ultra model in light, spring-ready colorways. Once again, classic style meets a contemporary sensibility with a mesh/nubuck upper construction, white panel overlays and Boost technology.
Release Date : March 23.
Price : Nothing confirmed, but previous releases came in around the $180 mark.
Availability : Look out for them coming to the adidas Originals website .
Editor’s Notes : There’s nothing groundbreaking here, but the triple white colorway and “Turbo Red” flashes make for a slick, slightly more adventurous alternative to the already released “ Muted ” pack.
